    <content lang="en">
      <city>Bern</city>
      <title>2023 budget: subsequent notifications of around CHF 4 billion</title>
      <lead>During its meeting on 26 October 2022, the Federal Council approved a subsequent notification for the 2023 budget. It includes additional burdens totalling CHF 4.05 billion, mainly attributable to the rescue mechanism for the electricity industry.</lead>
